asset.hookText:
Three-time world champion and double gold medalist Mo Farah, four-time American record holder Galen Rupp; and three-time winner of the Boston champion Rita Jeptoo have more in common than their monumental accolades. They share supernatural talent, sheer speed and an unwavering work ethic, and when it comes to the shoes they race and train in, they all choose to run on Zoom Air, Nike's fastest, most responsive Nike Air cushioning.

Learn more at http://www.nike.com/zoom
